messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning 项目的 attribute agent。
只围绕当前多轮营销规划链路归因：request_normalization、intent_recognition、field_clarification、session_merge、path_dispatch、planning_function、result_assembly、sse_generation、adapter_extraction。
优先定位最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段；如果 target_value_unit_probe、execution_stage_probe 或 planning_output_probe 已复现错误，必须以这些探针证据作为高优先级根因依据。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图正确识别为营销规划场景",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_recognition",
          "detail": "意图分类器将NBEV目标规划查询错误识别为其他意图（intent=4001），导致actual_stage=non_agent"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "intent_recognition 阶段的意图分类模型或规则未能正确识别营销规划意图，将用户明确的NBEV目标差距弥补请求误判为“其他意图”。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_recognition",
          "actual": "intent=4001, intent_name=其他意图, stage=non_agent",
          "expected": "规划类意图, stage=planning"
        },
        {
          "source": "execution_stage_probe",
          "detail": "intent_recognition stage evidence shows actual_stage=non_agent, expected_stage=planning"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "阶段路由正确：根据意图和字段状态进入规划或澄清阶段",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_recognition",
          "detail": "意图识别输出的stage被设置为non_agent，直接导致路由错误"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于上游意图识别失败，阶段路由逻辑依据错误的意图结果将请求送至non_agent，未进入planning或clarification。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "stage": "execution_trace",
          "detail": "extracted_output stage=non_agent; expected stage=planning or clarification"
        },
        {
          "source": "planning_output_probe",
          "detail": "actual_stage=null, stage_match=false"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "字段缺失时触发澄清交互",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "field_clarification",
          "detail": "由于intent_recognition导致未进入澄清流程，field_clarification虽标记succeeded但无实际澄清卡片生成"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别错误阻止了澄清流程的触发，系统未检测到字段缺失，因此未生成任何澄清卡片。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "stage": "field_clarification",
          "actual": "missing_fields=[], card_summary=[]",
          "expected": "missing_fields包含NBEV目标等必要字段，card_summary包含input_field_collection卡片"
        },
        {
          "source": "execution_stage_probe",
          "detail": "field_clarification stage evidence shows no missing_fields collected"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "SSE事件流协议完整且包含有效业务卡片",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "sse_generation",
          "detail": "SSE协议完整（completed=true）但card_summary为空，因无有效卡片可生成"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于前期意图识别和路由错误，planning或澄清卡片均未生成，导致SSE流中缺少业务内容，虽然协议完成但无意义。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "stage": "sse_generation",
          "actual": "card_summary=[], event_summary.completed=true",
          "expected": "card_summary非空且包含有效卡片"
        },
        {
          "source": "planning_output_probe",
          "detail": "actual_cards_count=0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "规划卡片具备可执行性：包含业务指标、目标值、时间范围与拆解维度",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_evaluable",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "planning_function",
          "detail": "因intent_recognition错误，planning_function并未实际执行规划逻辑（card_count=0）"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "规划卡片未生成，无法评估可执行性；根本原因是意图识别错误导致规划流程未启动。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "stage": "planning_function",
          "actual": "card_count=0, 无卡片",
          "expected": "应生成包含NBEV业务指标、队伍增长和产品组合维度的规划卡片"
        },
        {
          "source": "execution_stage_probe",
          "detail": "planning_function stage evidence shows card_count=0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "mp_contract:expected_stage",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_recognition",
          "detail": "意图识别输出stage=non_agent与reference contract期望的planning不符"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模块未能符合项目合同要求的expected_stage=planning，将请求路由至其他意图处理路径，违反了contract。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "planning_output_probe",
          "detail": "expected_stage=planning, actual_stage=null, stage_match=false"
        },
        {
          "source": "execution_stage_probe",
          "detail": "intent_recognition evidence shows actual_stage=non_agent vs expected_stage=planning"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    {
      "stage": "intent_recognition",
      "module": "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py or intent prompt/config",
      "reason": "意图分类错误导致stage=non_agent，是所有后续问题的根源"
    }
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "在intent_recognition阶段，意图分类器（可能基于规则或模型）错误地将用户关于NBEV目标差距和队伍/产品弥补策略的规划请求识别为“其他意图”（intent=4001），导致actual_stage被设为non_agent，而非预期的planning。此错误使下游path_dispatch、planning_function、field_clarification等均未按预期工作，最终未生成任何有效卡片，完全未能满足用户需求。因此，intent_recognition阶段的意图分类准确性是本次trace失败的根本原因。",
  "evidence": [
    {
      "execution_stage_probe": "intent_recognition stage: actual_stage=non_agent, expected_stage=planning"
    },
    {
      "planning_output_probe": "stage_match=false, actual_stage=null, actual_cards_count=0"
    },
    {
      "extracted_output": "intent=4001 (其他意图), stage=non_agent, card_summary=[]"
    },
    {
      "judge_result": "所有高优期望均未满足，blocking为true"
    }
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

